speech: Java Constructor  : It is used to initialize the instance of the object.	It does not have any return type. The default constructor is available to initialize the value.	The constructor's name is the same name as that of the class.	Java Method : It is used to expose the behaviour of an object.  It does have a return type. There is no default method is available. You can or cannot have the same name as that of the class.

data.text: Differentiate between Java constructor and Java method
